column5: https://youtu.be/Tl6A_6KSGt0Made a little video of us going out to check out the walleye in the river in northwest Ontario

Thanks for the footage. Interesting attempt to invade the walleye bedroom. Enjoyed the video, shows it is not as easy as it maybe can seem to get some action shots. My guess is that the spawn will be somewhat late this year, believe it is a factor of time, water temp, other. Bill
